des: "My kids do not like pumpkin pie, but they love to dip cookies in this dip. I've brought it to school for my daughter's class party and it was a big hit! Serve with assorted cookies for dipping."
ins: In a medium bowl, beat together cream cheese and marshmallow creme until smooth. Fold in pumpkin and cinnamon. Cover, and chill in the refrigerator until serving.
